Package ccre.ctrl

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDispatchJoystick
    A joystick that provides asynchronous triggers for its inputs, instead of pollable values.
    ISimpleJoystick
    A joystick that provides pollable channels for all of its inputs.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DriverImpls
    Contains various presets for driving the robot.
    Mixing
    Mixing is a class that provides a wide variety of useful static methods to accomplish various common actions using channels.
    ModeDispatcher
    A provider for a system that routes fired events along to one of a set of specified events based on the current 'mode' of the dispatcher.
    MultipleSourceBooleanController
    A controller that combines a series of registered BooleanOutputs or BooleanInputs to create a single output or input line.
